  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>🔥 Game Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧨 <strong>Turbojunk on Steroids</strong><br>Boost with turbines, overdrives, and explosive upgrades. Not just vehicles — real weapons on wheels.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 <strong>Boss Fights Included!</strong><br>Face deadly bosses in a story-driven campaign and prove who's king of the Wasteland.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Combat Racing</strong><br>Ram, shoot, blow up your enemies. This is war, not a race.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>Upgrade & Customize</strong><br>From brakes to monster turbo — build your perfect destruction machine.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>Dynamic Tracks</strong><br>Diverse environments with weather and terrain that affect how you drive: day/night cycles, fog, rain and more.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Modes for Every Player</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story Campaign – ~8 hours of explosive gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvE Challenges</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local Split-Screen & Online PvP</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick Race Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arena Mode – survive and destroy everything!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.webm?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.mp4?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯 <strong>Who is this game for?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turbo Sloths is made for fans of:</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twisted Metal, Crossout, FlatOut, SnowRunner</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tuning and upgrading powerful vehicles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Racing where you destroy, not dodge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hardcore, chaotic fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story modes with epic boss battles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💬 <strong>What players are saying</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“It’s Mad Max with turbo boosters and attitude.”<br>“A game that embraces madness.”<br>“Haven’t felt this kind of rush since FlatOut.”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.webm?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.mp4?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏁 Ready to race?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget what you know about racing.<br>Build your monster. Hit the track. Leave craters behind.<br>Turbo Sloths is waiting!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/b8e9c38116e0e92ed210183702dcad24.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/b8e9c38116e0e92ed210183702dcad24.webm?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/b8e9c38116e0e92ed210183702dcad24.mp4?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>🔥 Game Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧨 <strong>Turbojunk on Steroids</strong><br>Boost with turbines, overdrives, and explosive upgrades. Not just vehicles — real weapons on wheels.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 <strong>Boss Fights Included!</strong><br>Face deadly bosses in a story-driven campaign and prove who's king of the Wasteland.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Combat Racing</strong><br>Ram, shoot, blow up your enemies. This is war, not a race.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>Upgrade & Customize</strong><br>From brakes to monster turbo — build your perfect destruction machine.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>Dynamic Tracks</strong><br>Diverse environments with weather and terrain that affect how you drive: day/night cycles, fog, rain and more.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Modes for Every Player</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story Campaign – ~8 hours of explosive gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvE Challenges</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local Split-Screen & Online PvP</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick Race Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arena Mode – survive and destroy everything!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.webm?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/5345b066bc2feaa83678ac9724335ede.mp4?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯 <strong>Who is this game for?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turbo Sloths is made for fans of:</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twisted Metal, Crossout, FlatOut, SnowRunner</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tuning and upgrading powerful vehicles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Racing where you destroy, not dodge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hardcore, chaotic fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story modes with epic boss battles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💬 <strong>What players are saying</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“It’s Mad Max with turbo boosters and attitude.”<br>“A game that embraces madness.”<br>“Haven’t felt this kind of rush since FlatOut.”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.webm?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/7d2d36e2fb4b8f612c6273828bd0ab04.mp4?t=1771603980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏁 Ready to race?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget what you know about racing.<br>Build your monster. Hit the track. Leave craters behind.<br>Turbo Sloths is waiting!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1443630/extras/b8e9c38116e0e92ed210183702dcad24.poster.avif?t=1771603980\" width=700 heigh